      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new owner to enjoy it as much as I have. This car is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and is spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been kept in truly pristine condition, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
