    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly desirable 3.8L flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and exceptional thermal efficiency, paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing superior damping and mechanical grip. This example is free of bore scoring and shows zero evidence of oil seepage or suspension bushing fatigue. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its factory depth, while the cabin shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies the vehicle, documenting a rigorous preventative maintenance regimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
