    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe reinforced, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance that defined this chassis. With a pristine underbody and zero mechanical lash, this example is a definitive benchmark for the naturally aspirated M-division era.",
